---
title: Baby Corn and Green Bean Curry with Toasted Cashews and Jasmine Rice
description: This delicious and beautifully fragrant dish is super easy and quick to prepare. We particularly love the baby corn. Fun fact: Baby corn is simply corn that been harvested while corn stalks are still young and immature!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baby-corn-and-green-bean-curry-fc7cd3d0.jpg
